An application where users can create, read and update

Interface
  user can view form
  user can submit order
  user can edit order
  user can delete order

User class
  attributes "name, password"
  user sign up/ login
  has many orders

User controller and views
  render sign up form
  process sign up form, create user or post
  render login form
  process login form
  set session
  can view the orders

Order class
  how much water in a day

Order controller and views
  render new order form
  submit order
  render all order
  render one instance
  render update form and instance
  update instance
  deletes instance

Procedure
  set up classes
  set up my database
  users controller
  the order
